sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant W as Web App
    participant C as Sepolia (Factory + Project)
    participant E as ENS
    participant S as Walrus
    participant L as Local Cache

    rect rgb(255,248,240)
    Note over U,S: Provenance view (/art/[artworkENS])
    U->>W: Open artwork page
    W->>L: Load cached manifest (if present)
    W->>E: Read artwork ENS text records
    W->>S: Fetch manifest + render via blob proxy
    alt ENS records incomplete/missing
      W->>C: Resolve project + read ownerOf/tokenENS/tokenURI
      W->>S: Fetch token metadata image
    end
    W-->>U: Show render, manifest, ENS records, on-chain fallback
    end

    rect rgb(248,248,255)
    Note over U,S: Home exploration (/)
    U->>W: Open home
    W->>C: Read factory allProjectsLength + allProjects
    loop latest collections
      W->>C: Read project name/artistENS/collectionENS/mint stats
      W->>S: Fetch algorithm bundle preview
    end
    loop latest minted works
      W->>C: Read ownerOf/tokenENS/tokenURI
      W->>S: Fetch metadata/image
    end
    W-->>U: Display latest collections and latest works
    end
